%A4%E5%85%83%E4%BB%B6-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">&lt;template&gt; 包裹指令元件</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#v-if-%E8%88%87-v-show-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">v-if 與 v-show</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2%E5%B7%AE%E7%95%B0-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">特色差異</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#CSS-%E9%9A%B1%E8%97%8F%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">CSS 隱藏機制</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Vue3 屬性綁定 (v-bind)","uid":"a7724faeac3358712c7d20b51cf57625","slug":"Vue3-屬性綁定-v-bind","date":"2021-07-28T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Vue3-屬性綁定-v-bind.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"綁定屬性 v-bindv-bind 來綁定圖片： 綁定 imageUrl 來快速更改圖片網址， 綁定 title 滑鼠游標移上去時會出現圖片名稱 範例程式碼： &lt;img v-bind:src&#x3D;&quot;breakfastShop.imgUrl&quot; v-b...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.5k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/categories/Vue.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"Vue3 渲染方式 (v-for)","uid":"9c11d646618f3595bbe1f004add8eb99","slug":"Vue3-渲染方式-v